    loadHistoricalTraceGrids(
  files,
  vars = NULL,
  lonLim = c(-25, 25),
  latLim = c(25, 50),
  start_date = "1551-01-01",
  end_date = "1990-12-31",
  years = 1961:1990,
  dictionary = system.file("extdata", "TraCE21ka_dictionary.csv", package =
    "TraCE21kaDSR"),
  selection_vars = c("tas", "tasmax", "tasmin", "hurs@992.5561", "ps", "pr", "cld",
    "wss"),
  compute_wss = TRUE
)
